# --- Vendored Debug build (project decision 2026-07-18) ---
# Ship the compiled C# execution server so non-developers can run SolidPilot
# without building it. Debug (not Release): the project is under active development
# and each build is validated locally before push. Runtime *.log stays out.
!solidworks-execution/SolidworksExecution/bin/
solidworks-execution/SolidworksExecution/bin/*
!solidworks-execution/SolidworksExecution/bin/Debug/
!solidworks-execution/SolidworksExecution/bin/Debug/**
solidworks-execution/SolidworksExecution/bin/Debug/*.log


